title: About paying Smart contract audit fees
body:
We submitted
1.OKMoon
2.SLS
3.SLS Farm
The audit of the smart contract, the audit has passed the preliminary inspection, we need to pass 0x40752e930f26A9A5B03560cb756fA7598B20BC5b to sell OKMoon worth 3500USD to pay the audit fee
(The OKMoon of 0x40752e930f26A9A5B03560cb756fA7598B20BC5b is all purchased from the Kswap market)
